        "answer": "先在每条 Activity 记录上计算 MIN(event_date) OVER (PARTITION BY player_id) AS first_date，再按 player_id 聚合，用 MAX(CASE WHEN event_date = DATE_ADD(first_date, INTERVAL 1 DAY) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) 得到这个玩家是否留存，最后 SUM(retained) / COUNT(*)。"
